summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing construction of Contract No. 3 of the Lake Washington North - Unit 1, Sewer Separation Project and of approximately 380 feet of sanitary sewers within said project area, for the separation of existing combined sewers in the area bounded generally by 35th Avenue East on the east, by East John Street on the north, by 23rd Avenue East on the west, and East Alder Street on the south, and making an appropriation from the Sewer Improvement Fund therefor.
